{
  "stem": "13469.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was not very nice kind of thing, because they could see who we were, and we could see who they were.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, they looked like SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, some of them might have had their uniforms on, and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they all spoke German, and they clicked their heels.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were Germans, all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And whilst the Dutch authorities tried to figure out who we were-- and we gave them names of lots of people, lots of friends of our parents who would vouch for us-- in the meantime, Eve-- we'd contacted a lady called [NON-ENGLISH], Aunt [NON-ENGLISH], who lived below us in [NON-ENGLISH] in Amsterdam [INAUDIBLE] who always looked after Eve.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is another bit that I forgot about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I must just go back to this bit in Amsterdam, then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Amsterdam, there was, of course, one other opportunity-- apart from being deported-- and that was to go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and we had the opportunity to go into hiding in, in Holland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had many Dutch friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My parents had very good friends, and many of them offered to hide us, either in Amsterdam or, or elsewhere in the countryside in Holland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But going into hiding was extremely risky, not only for the Jews who went into hiding, but also for the Dutch citizens who, who were doing the hiding.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They could be sent to the Dutch concentration camps or could be shot, et cetera, or-- It was difficult.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my father, again, never wanted to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He, being-- sticking to the rules, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He, he wouldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My mother, I think, would've gone for the going into hiding, like the Franks did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were in exactly the same opportunities.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
